{"tid":2020286,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"鍾南山：中國有第二波爆發風險　武漢曾隱瞞關鍵資訊","createTime":"2020-05-17T03:05:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-17T06:22:48.000Z","uid":81228,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"066a1a570b95a6a50a8d86f5bd95559a8fac7d47","tid":2020286,"uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T03:05:58.000Z","msg":"中國工程院院士鍾南山接受外媒《CNN》專訪時表示，中國仍面對新冠肺炎疫情第2次爆發的「巨大挑戰」。他同時提到，武漢地方政府在疫情爆發之初曾隱瞞關鍵資訊，但中央政府在1月下旬開始主導應對疫情後，官方數據都正確無誤。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/20200407/324155316042338304.jpeg/dEz1beXtL5XeTFIigDwtU7q8WvZ4rYk429-Xitvfl4o?v=w1280\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F20200407%2F324155316042338304.jpeg%2FdEz1beXtL5XeTFIigDwtU7q8WvZ4rYk429-Xitvfl4o%3Fv%3Dw1280&h=0716eebf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n鍾南山認為，中國仍有第二波爆發風險。（中新社）<br />\n<br />\n《CNN》報道，內地目前已漸漸恢復正常生活、放寬防疫管制措施，且全國各地陸續復工復學。但鍾南山表示，當局不該自滿，因為爆發第二波疫情的風險越來越大，最近幾周，武漢市、東北部的黑龍江省和吉林省都出現群聚感染事件。<br />\n<br />\n他說，因大多數中國民眾缺乏抗體，仍容易感染病毒，「目前我們仍面臨巨大挑戰，狀況不比外國好。」<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/20200322/318493771006349312.jpeg/GCY1ipJK2y9N734atoNMoSwo715fJws5_fw5hP38OYQ?v=w1280\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F20200322%2F318493771006349312.jpeg%2FGCY1ipJK2y9N734atoNMoSwo715fJws5_fw5hP38OYQ%3Fv%3Dw1280&h=982e69b8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n鍾南山亦坦承，武漢地方政府在去年12月疫情爆發時，封鎖有關疫情爆發的關鍵細節。（中新社）<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/20200312/314810268658044928.jpeg/B0NyAJlcJJ6B82SPM-WHdc1Kfj0SteDVWFgidlhYInY?v=w640\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F20200312%2F314810268658044928.jpeg%2FB0NyAJlcJJ6B82SPM-WHdc1Kfj0SteDVWFgidlhYInY%3Fv%3Dw640&h=fa8dfc10&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/20200314/315441667593342976.jpeg/pVSmF9WZCqXMvOu7Z6JvKNBIpghMF0saM07jHDNO4xw?v=w640\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F20200314%2F315441667593342976.jpeg%2FpVSmF9WZCqXMvOu7Z6JvKNBIpghMF0saM07jHDNO4xw%3Fv%3Dw640&h=b7ed710e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n鍾南山亦坦承，武漢地方政府在去年12月疫情爆發時，封鎖有關疫情的關鍵細節，他率領專家小組在1月18日到當地調查時，收到很多醫生和學生指情況比官方公布的嚴重，當地政府不願意說實話（They didn't like to tell the truth）。<br />\n<br />\n鍾南山憶述，武漢官方報告稱病例持續十天以上仍為41宗，但海外確診人數卻開始增加，於是起了疑心，「我不相信這個結果，所以（一直）問，必須給我真實的數字。 我認為他們很不願意回答我的問題。」<br />\n<br />\n※1月下旬，年屆83歲的鍾南山臨危受命趕往武漢防疫最前線，此後又多次出席記者會交代疫情防控進展，其身體狀態看上去絲毫不遜色於年輕人，得益於他幾十年如一日的鍛鍊：<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20200517/338642289947709440.jpeg/fqW8eBOQGm6zMVIUBoHtOnRwwAAAp8x-CQjlPAkI5Tw?v=w640\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20200517%2F338642289947709440.jpeg%2FfqW8eBOQGm6zMVIUBoHtOnRwwAAAp8x-CQjlPAkI5Tw%3Fv%3Dw640&h=830b295e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/20200403/322846004581896192.jpeg/JUrC_ZB713-wsSZjlSiR0VzyOTwiL80_G1GfQBtRn0A?v=w640\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F20200403%2F322846004581896192.jpeg%2FJUrC_ZB713-wsSZjlSiR0VzyOTwiL80_G1GfQBtRn0A%3Fv%3Dw640&h=fab079f2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/20200403/322846006729379840.jpeg/vuKOmDdIg6nFlWR8WKsm8CqOGon6DiYdKbW0bim1tG4?v=w640\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F20200403%2F322846006729379840.jpeg%2FvuKOmDdIg6nFlWR8WKsm8CqOGon6DiYdKbW0bim1tG4%3Fv%3Dw640&h=4c8d5c46&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/20200403/322846008704897025.jpeg/v2c2_jLhtYge4iepLktFt5ZJZoCWrkWfiggLiIoIC4g?v=w640\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F20200403%2F322846008704897025.jpeg%2Fv2c2_jLhtYge4iepLktFt5ZJZoCWrkWfiggLiIoIC4g%3Fv%3Dw640&h=9196492e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/20200403/322846010646859776.jpeg/bujZODEHSykb7liOONgUV_DlSW9Y4wrpjWKoDo1iqA4?v=w640\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F20200403%2F322846010646859776.jpeg%2FbujZODEHSykb7liOONgUV_DlSW9Y4wrpjWKoDo1iqA4%3Fv%3Dw640&h=8caadecd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/20200403/322846014807609344.jpeg/FZxXMsAZyrzyD2DCMBz93C0XxG8jQlBqhM5nLYTOZy0?v=w640\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F20200403%2F322846014807609344.jpeg%2FFZxXMsAZyrzyD2DCMBz93C0XxG8jQlBqhM5nLYTOZy0%3Fv%3Dw640&h=79136aef&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n但鍾南山認為，中央政府在1月下旬開始主導應對疫情後，官方數據都正確無誤。<br />\n<br />\n他表示，中國政府17年前就從SARS疫情中學到教訓，當時就是因為「隱瞞部分疫情長達兩、三個月」。因此，中央政府這次宣布「所有城市、所有政府部門都應通報真實數字，否則會受到懲罰」，「所以從1月23日以後，我想所有數據都是正確的」。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20200517/338624922496667648.jpeg/BcI1kLmrrNLf3_S5YVyHS2_PBKEtCacr5gGAY-YBgGM?v=w1280\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20200517%2F338624922496667648.jpeg%2FBcI1kLmrrNLf3_S5YVyHS2_PBKEtCacr5gGAY-YBgGM%3Fv%3Dw1280&h=ffb8e6eb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n鍾南山認為，中央政府在1月下旬開始主導應對疫情後，官方數據都正確無誤。圖為國務院副總理、中央指導組組長孫春蘭，在疫情期間率中央指導組成員在武漢街頭視察。（中新社）<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20200427/331454015571365888.jpeg/3yxbaOZPisbBaqpyRUVxETr7YMIMsSFOgDafGIA2nxg?v=w640\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20200427%2F331454015571365888.jpeg%2F3yxbaOZPisbBaqpyRUVxETr7YMIMsSFOgDafGIA2nxg%3Fv%3Dw640&h=acddc965&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20200517/338625845373571072.jpeg/UOGpilrZRimdpaw4pSMVr429oqw7_NroMvdRBjL3UQY?v=w640\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20200517%2F338625845373571072.jpeg%2FUOGpilrZRimdpaw4pSMVr429oqw7_NroMvdRBjL3UQY%3Fv%3Dw640&h=a5513ed4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n鍾南山亦不同意美國總統特朗普與國務卿蓬佩奧指，病毒來自武漢病毒研究所的說法。他指出，武漢病毒研究所學者石正麗是他的好友，關於病毒是該研究所製造並外洩的說法，他曾多次詢問石正麗，「她指這說法太荒謬，她從來沒做過那樣的東西」，「她說以他們目前的設備和人力&hellip;&hellip;是做不出人造病毒」。<br />\n<br />\n他強調，中國疾控中心2月初曾花2星期調查石正麗的實驗室是否出了差錯，但沒找到任何結果。<br />\n<br />\n（CNN）<br />\n撰文：崔德興"},{"pid":"73046570ff5a7cc0aa6407fa7fe1639d1b5d927a","tid":2020286,"uid":343754,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T03:09:05.000Z","msg":"前排好似話封返城<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f991dd0531d743664169c439caa8d5f698ce23a","tid":2020286,"uid":227628,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T05:18:03.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">「所以從1月23日以後，我想所有數據都是正確的」。</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n武漢幾萬骨灰邊度嚟？"},{"pid":"0e72a0cc0d87001dae813c713565814c65892be0","tid":2020286,"uid":15815,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T06:21:36.000Z","msg":"武漢地方政府在疫情爆發之初曾隱瞞關鍵資訊<br />\n<br />\n食死貓<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed2d52ae7d0cca107b683df3c9b625e2623bb519","tid":2020286,"uid":357803,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T06:22:48.000Z","msg":"佢根本控制唔到疫情，自己放毒，真係捉蟲入屎忽"}]}